"Do I Know This Already?" Quiz

9. The correct answer is "firewall-cmd --list-all-zones".

Ordering

Steps 4 and 5 are in the wrong order with respect to each other.  "Deny" rules
are processed before "allow" rules.

Configuring Masquerading

IPv6 masquerading can be used with firewalld, but not with the
"--add-masquerade" option.  It requires the use of a rich rule or direct rule
that includes the "masquerade" action and address family ipv6.
